snippet.title: Shot Online is now available on Steam
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/390090/Shot_Online/

Shot-Online is a reproduction of the full experience and game of golf in full, rich 3D graphics.
It is not just an online sports game either, but it is a highly accurate simulation and a deep role-playing experience. It is the RPG quality that makes Shot-Online the unique game it is, especially with the community interaction and the enhancement and leveling of your character.

#Shotonline #Golf #Golfgame #Simulation #Sports #role-playing #GrandLaunch #OfficialRelease #SteamLaunch
